text: René Marteaux (born 3 August 1929) is a Belgian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Belgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belgium Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Saint-Gilles, Belgium
